## Reporting Multiple Errors

.background images/hard-work.png

- It turned out that the project returns multiple errors.
- They are all about the same error in the input.
- Just reporting from different levels (adding context).
- Can't be so hard to change that...


## Reporting Multiple Errors

.background images/sleepless.png

- It turned out that it's not a matter of "a loop in the right place".
- I have to try harder in different ways.


## Reporting Multiple Errors

